<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>이글이글</title>
        <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css'/>
        <script type='text/javascript' src ='/javascripts/jquery-1.8.1.min.js'></script>
        <script type='text/javascript' src ='/socket.io/socket.io.js'></script>
	    <script>
			function enterRoom(groupName){
				location.href='/join/'+groupName+'/<%= character %>';
			};
	    </script>
    </head>
    <body>
		<p><img src='/images/<%= character %>.png' class='character'/></p>
		<p><%= nickName %>님 환영합니다.</p>
		<h2>이글이글 그룹 목록</h2>
		<% if(groupList && groupList.length){ %>
		<table>
			<col width='100px'/>
			<col />
		<% for(var i=0;i<groupList.length;i++){ %>
			<tr>
				<td><%= groupList[i].name %></td>
		    	<td><input type='button' value='입장' onClick="enterRoom('<%= groupList[i].name %>');"/></td>
		    </tr>
		 <% } %>
	    <% } %>
	    </table>
		<p>원하는 그룹이 없으면 새로운 그룹을 만드세요.</p>
		<form action='/makegroup' method='POST'>
		    <label for='groupName'>그룹명</label>
		    <input type='text' id='groupName' name='groupName'/>
		    <input type='hidden' name='character' value='<%= character %>'/>
		    <input type='submit' value='그룹 만들기'/>
		</form>
	</body>
</html>